HEADWORD: Standish
<hw>Stand"ish</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Stand</ets> +
<ets>dish</ets>.]</ety> <def>A stand, or case, for pen and
ink.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I bequeath to Dean Swift, Esq., my large silver
<qex>standish</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

